Cell.Text: I don't know you. You in Riften lookin' for trouble?

Node.ToolTip:

Last User:ananes Date:3/22/2011 File:Skyrim.esm

Cell.Text: [S] Yeah? Well, I got news for you; there's nothing to see here. | Last thing the Black-Briars need is some stranger stickin' their nose where it doesn't belong.

Node.Caption: DialogueRiftenMaulSceneBranchTopic01: Just passing through.

Node.ToolTip:
000649D8 - Custom, in use by ananes
Last User:ananes Date:3/22/2011 File:Skyrim.esm

Cell.Text: [S] Don't say something you'll regret. | Last thing the Black-Briars need is some loudmouth tryin' to meddle in their affairs.

Node.Caption: DialogueRiftenMaulSceneBranchTopic02: What's it to you?

Node.ToolTip:
000649D7 - Custom, in use by ananes
Last User:ananes Date:3/22/2011 File:Skyrim.esm

Cell.Text: [S] That's the wrong answer. | Last thing the Black-Briars need around here is some troublemaker tryin' to steal a piece of the action.

Node.Caption: DialogueRiftenMaulSceneBranchTopic03: I'm not scared of you.

Cell.Text: The Black-Briar's have Riften in their pocket and the Thieves Guild watchin' their back, so keep your nose out of their business. | Me? I'm Maul; I watch the streets for them. If you need dirt on anythin', I'm your guy... but it'll cost you.
[S] You can pretend not to hear me all you want... but you better stay out of the Black-Briar's business.

Node.ToolTip:
000649D4 - Custom, in use by ananes
Last User:ananes Date:3/22/2011 File:Skyrim.esm

Cell.Text: [S] Then we're speakin' the same language. Good. | So what do you want to know?
[S] G|Then you're stupider than you look. | You better watch your ass around here.

Node.Caption: DialogueRiftenMaulSceneBranch02Topic01: Dirt, huh? Not exactly clean myself. (Persuade)

Node.ToolTip:
000649D3 - Custom, in use by ananes
Last User:ananes Date:3/22/2011 File:Skyrim.esm

Cell.Text: [S] Pleasure doin' business with you. | So what do you want to know?
You don't have enough to earn my loyalty.

Node.Caption: DialogueRiftenMaulSceneBranch02Topic02: Here, what can you tell me? ( Gold)

Node.ToolTip:
000649D2 - Custom, in use by ananes
Last User:ananes Date:3/22/2011 File:Skyrim.esm

Cell.Text: [S] All right, all right, let's not get too hasty now. | So what do you want to know?
[S] G|Ha ha! Don't make me laugh. | Just stay out of the Black-Briar's affairs. You'll live longer.

Node.Caption: DialogueRiftenMaulSceneBranch02Topic03: How about you tell me for free? (Intimidate)

Node.ToolTip:
000649D1 - Custom, in use by ananes
Last User:ananes Date:3/22/2011 File:Skyrim.esm

Cell.Text: [S] G|Suit yourself. | I'll be at the docks if you change your mind.

Node.Caption: DialogueRiftenMaulSceneBranch02Topic04: I'll just stay out of your way.

Cell.Text: [S] G|Yeah, walk away like a good doggie. Just stay out of the Black-Briar's business and maybe we'll give you a bone.
[S] Only way you could have found one of those is by stealin' it. Guess you'll fit in around here better than I thought. | So what do you want to know?

Node.Caption: DialogueRiftenMaulSceneBranch02Topic05: Got any dirt on this? (Show Mysterious Jewel)
